OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLight winds
OL,6,Fand sunny spells to end the day.
OL,7,FHowever, cloud will increase from the
OL,8,Fwest overnight, with a little light
OL,9,Frain or showers possible later over
OL,10,Fwestern hills. A slightly milder night
OL,11,Funder the blanket of cloud.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FRather cloudy to start the
OL,14,Fday, the cloud then tending to break
OL,15,Fup a little allowing frequent showers
OL,16,Fto develop, some heavy with thunder
OL,17,Fpossible towards the north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
