OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,6,Fmostly dry, settled spell of weather
OL,7,Fwith bright or sunny spells. A spell
OL,8,Fof rain likely into Thursday.
OL,9,FTemperatures near average, but slowly
OL,10,Fedging up.
